					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">jrlepage wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Somehow I suspect you're being a prick on purpose.</div><br />Don't worry... Bregalad sometimes has a hard time seeing things from a perspective other than his own (if people do things differently from him it takes him some time to understand that, well, people are different and have different opinions and tastes), but he's not a bad person and would not be a jerk just to piss people off.<br /><br />I get him though... for us, who like to make games for the NES, it may sound weird that for other people it's just a musical instrument. But this is a fact, so we just have to deal with it. I assure you that this community has nothing against free speech! =)</div>

