				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p99508">Re: NSF PCM technique (via Deflemask)</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=99508&amp;sid=ee47864c3bb022961a4c4b5dd6ff35c9#p99508"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Thu Sep 13, 2012 10:04 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
